{"title":"邻接表与链式前向星","uid":"9c00a08911d8154db7483d2127231c8c","slug":"邻接表与链式前向星","date":"2026-01-27T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2026-01-28T16:43:25.448Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/邻接表与链式前向星.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"邻接表\"><a href=\"#邻接表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"邻接表\"></a>邻接表</h1><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title class_\">node</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">//所需存的成员</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> v,w;<span class=\"comment\">//v是该点指向的终点，w是这条边的权</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">vector&lt;node&gt; a[n];<span class=\"comment\">//建立一个含有n个vector的数组</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">那么，a[i][j]表示的是，与第i个节点相邻的第j个node</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"链式前向星\"><a href=\"#链式前向星\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"链式前向星\"></a>链式前向星</h1><p>我们使用四个数组来存储有关信息，其中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">head[i]表示第i个节点最后/最先存入的边</span><br><span class=\"line\">v[i]表示第i条边指向的终点</span><br><span class=\"line\">w[i]表示第i条边的权</span><br><span class=\"line\">next[i]表示一个代表边的下标，这条边与第i条边是同一个起点，且存入顺序是第i条边的上一条/下一条。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"遍历边\"><a href=\"#遍历边\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"遍历边\"></a>遍历边</h2><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"type\">int</span> i = head[u]; i != <span class=\"number\">-1</span>; i = nxt[i])&#123;<span class=\"comment\">//i!=-1与~i是一样的。这里的-1是一个默认值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    此时i代表的就是，所有从节点u出发的边</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> vv = v[i];<span class=\"comment\">//vv[i]即这条边的终点</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">double</span> ww = w[i]<span class=\"comment\">//ww[i]即这条边的权</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","feature":true,"text":"邻接表123456struct node{ //所需存的成员 int v,w;//v是该点指向的终点，w是这条边的权};vector<node> a[n];//...","permalink":"/post/邻接表与链式前向星","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":460,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"算法","slug":"算法","count":12,"path":"api/categories/算法.json"},{"name":"模板","slug":"算法/模板","count":7,"path":"api/categories/算法/模板.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"图","slug":"图","count":1,"path":"api/tags/图.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%82%BB%E6%8E%A5%E8%A1%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">邻接表</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%93%BE%E5%BC%8F%E5%89%8D%E5%90%91%E6%98%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">链式前向星</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E8%BE%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">遍历边</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"LHY","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/256316666?s=400&u=531212165de7b7b90dc6ec2dd44404fc88f4a435&v=4","link":"/","description":"天空中的宝石应该交由天空去寻找","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"